{"tid":1742732,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"攬炒的意思係大家都冚家鏟，無工返係必然的事! 無可能只炒權貴而自己相安無事","createTime":"2019-11-21T02:05:05.000Z","updateTime":"2019-11-21T05:09:54.000Z","uid":18074,"like":13,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":18,"replies":[{"pid":"eb90afdb9fa86f36298ad78bb387eaa4970db477","tid":1742732,"uid":18074,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-21T02:05:05.000Z","msg":"講真，如果自己無失業無收入的覺悟，就唔好話自己支持攬炒<br />\n<br />\n黎明運動的作用在於被罷工，影響商業運作（商場無人行，工司無人做嘢，遊客唔敢嚟），從而達致經濟攬炒的局面<br />\n<br />\n普羅市民一定受影響，而且係最先受影響。呢個幾星期的黎明活動，令出面舖頭生意少咗幾多，大家有眼見<br />\n<br />\n口講支持一定容易，但當真係燒到埋身，仲做唔做到不割席，大家要諗下"},{"pid":"af3c06c0c0d4be9c1018dc8d9e83eabd03400be7","tid":1742732,"uid":18074,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-21T02:05:32.000Z","msg":"1/10"},{"pid":"e7a968838b30ca6e774aa88590cd8ce924e77cf0","tid":1742732,"uid":18074,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-21T02:05:42.000Z","msg":"2/10"},{"pid":"de99b23d6a59f64dd0341e00a84ba80ff7440489","tid":1742732,"uid":18074,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-21T02:05:54.000Z","msg":"3/10"},{"pid":"fd8d366bedc0dbeb23985edd9c5382f8d2d0620f","tid":1742732,"uid":18074,"like":1,"dislike":1,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-21T02:06:22.000Z","msg":"當然，公墓園會係少數的倖存者"},{"pid":"8a1f78f374ec2e2afb6dc5ecc2a681560e83c68c","tid":1742732,"uid":45007,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-21T02:06:28.000Z","msg":"燒吧燒吧<br />\n就算自焚<br />\n我必攬住藍絲一起燒"},{"pid":"c27faeca666042c1d09a23470331bf1ddf9d6f05","tid":1742732,"uid":18074,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-21T02:06:32.000Z","msg":"4/10"},{"pid":"dd6ba21f524d75c19542a0ae1365ea4af5c19b00","tid":1742732,"uid":337607,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-21T02:06:45.000Z","msg":"一直都覺得。。。"},{"pid":"b41f99863724dffebf2d43ac03cc4586eb84b631","tid":1742732,"uid":18074,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-21T02:06:46.00